    "unit_type": "edited_selection",
    "label": "English Songs in Manuscript Selden B. 26",
    "scope_note": "The cataloged unit is Frederick Morgan Padelford's thirty-one numbered English-song transcriptions from Bodleian MS Arch. Selden B. 26 together with the interleaved variant and comparison apparatus represented by CME00104 on printed pages 86-115. It is not the complete 1912 article, whose title and introduction occupy pages 79-85; not all English verse in the Selden manuscript; not all 53 musical compositions in the relevant component; not the complete composite codex; and not the U-M encoding or repository XML as digital artifacts."
  },
